<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="earnest-adj">earnest <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɜːnɪst/    美 /'ɜːrnɪst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>非常认真的；诚挚的；真诚的</strong></h4>
<p>very serious and sincere：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is so earnest over his studies.
他学习非常认真。</p></div></div>